            {
              "id": "CVE-2026-4926",
              "name": "OsPackageVulnerability",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "CVE-2026-4926: Inefficient Regular Expression Complexity"
              },
              "helpUri": "https://scout.docker.com/v/CVE-2026-4926?s=github&n=path-to-regexp&t=npm&vr=%3E%3D8.0.0%2C%3C8.4.0",
              "help": {
                "text": "### Impact\n\nA bad regular expression is generated any time you have multiple sequential optional groups (curly brace syntax), such as `{a}{b}{c}:z`. The generated regex grows exponentially with the number of groups, causing denial of service.\n\n### Patches\n\nFixed in version 8.4.0.\n\n### Workarounds\n\nLimit the number of sequential optional groups in route patterns. Avoid passing user-controlled input as route patterns.\n",
                "markdown": "> ### Impact\n\nA bad regular expression is generated any time you have multiple sequential optional groups (curly brace syntax), such as `{a}{b}{c}:z`. The generated regex grows exponentially with the number of groups, causing denial of service.\n\n### Patches\n\nFixed in version 8.4.0.\n\n### Workarounds\n\nLimit the number of sequential optional groups in route patterns. Avoid passing user-controlled input as route patterns.\n\n|                                                                                                             |\n|Package                                                                        pkg:npm/path-to-regexp@8.3.0  |\n|Affected range                                                                 >=8.0.0,<8.4.0                |\n|Fixed version                                                                  8.4.0                         |\n|[[CVSS Score 7.5] [CVSS Vector CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:H]]                                |\n"
              },
              "properties": {
                "affected_version": ">=8.0.0,<8.4.0",
                "cvssV3": 7.5,
                "cvssV3_severity": "HIGH",
                "cvssV3_vector": "CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:H",
                "fixed_version": "8.4.0",
                "purls": [
                  "pkg:npm/path-to-regexp@8.3.0"
